title: Ep. -288 - HARD KNOCKS ON HBO END OF KEEPING UP WITH THE KARDASHIANS
description:
Scott Patton reviews this season of HBO’s Hard Knocks. This season gives an unfiltered all-access look at what it takes to make it in the National Football League. The 18-time Sports Emmy Award winning series follows head coaches Anthony Lynn of the Los Angeles Chargers and Sean McVay of the Los Angeles Rams as they lead a mix of established veterans, free-agent acquisitions, and rising stars on both sides of the ball.

 

Kathleen and Natalie from Say Bible podcast help Kate discuss the Kardashian’s announcement this week that the final season of KUWTK would air in early 2021.

 

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
